---
const today = new Date();
import CalFloatingButton from './CalFloatingButton.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
import PopupModal from './PopupModal.astro';
---

<footer>
  <div class="footer-content">
    <small>
      &copy;{today.getFullYear()} {SITE_TITLE}. All rights reserved.
      <button id="open-privacy" class="button-to-link">Privacy Notice</button>
    </small>

<PopupModal id="privacy" title="Privacy Notice">
  <p>This site is operated from the EU and follows GDPR guidelines.</p>

  <section>
    <h3>What we collect</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>If you subscribe, we collect your full name and email via Brevo (with double opt-in).</li>
      <li>Booking a meeting via Cal.com may collect your name and email.</li>
	  <li>Stripe will process payment details like name, email, and billing info once payments are enabled. Currently, no payments are handled.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h3>Cookies (Third-party only)</h3>
    <p>
      We do not use tracking, analytics, or ad cookies.  
      Only essential cookies may be set by embedded third-party services:  
      <a href="https://www.brevo.com/legal/privacypolicy/" target="_blank">Brevo</a>,  
      <a href="https://stripe.com/privacy" target="_blank">Stripe</a>,  
      <a href="https://cal.com/privacy" target="_blank">Cal.com</a>,  
      <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank">Cloudflare</a>,  
      <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-privacy-statement" target="_blank">GitHub</a>.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h3>Hosting and delivery</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> improves performance, encryption, and protection. It may set technical cookies.</li>
      <li><strong>GitHub Pages</strong> hosts this site. GitHub may log IPs for basic operations, but no personal data is accessed or used by the site owner.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h3>Your rights</h3>
    <p>You may request access, updates, or deletion of your data at any time by emailing  
      <a href="mailto:info@t1grid.com">info@t1grid.com</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
  
  </PopupModal>

</footer>

